    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/nagaraja-credibility-assessment-team",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 credibility factors meet or exceed the required level. The single shortfall in Test conditions (achieved Gradation 2 vs. required Gradation 3) is accepted on the basis that the single F1717 test condition is the standard regulatory benchmark and additional load conditions are outside the current submission scope. Overall model credibility is sufficient for the intended regulatory decision.",
